                      <span>33</span>
                      votes <span class="ItemCaption">Reviewed: </span>
                      <span>2003-10-15</span>
                    </div>
                    <span>If you are interested in Bourne or Bash shell programming, be aware that this book focuses exclusively on the Korn shell (ksh or "ksh93"). The Korn shell is a superset of the Bourne shell, but if you want to write scripts for sh (Bourne) or bash, another book might be more appropriate.</span>
                  
              
